1
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:21,600
Mr. Lin,

2
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:26,240
someone just delivered this to you.

3
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,400
Why are you so nervous?

4
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,560
What do you mean?

5
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:24,680
You don't want to admit it?

6
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,600
Give me some time.

7
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:31,840
I'll think about it.

8
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:33,960
Alright.

9
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,040
Then you get some rest.

10
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:37,440
I have something to do.

11
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:03,920
Hello?

12
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,120
Where's Lu Xing?

13
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:25,840
Lu Xing?

14
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,040
Do you know him?

15
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:30,000
Cut the crap.

16
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,920
Has he come to you?

17
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,600
I thought he was important to you.

18
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:42,400
It seems not.

19
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:44,840
What do you mean?

20
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:45,960
What happened to Xing?

21
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:47,800
What's your relationship?

22
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:53,320
He's been missing for three days.

23
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,640
As for our relationship,

24
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:57,680
he is just

25
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,360
he's just a dog I picked up.

26
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,360
Say something!

27
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,840
Are you mute?

28
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,840
Do you know your life is mine?

29
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:36,680
If you don't tell me the truth,

30
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:37,840
I'll throw you out right now.

31
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,080
Stay by my side.

32
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,640
I'm the only one who can help you now.

33
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,840
[So he sacrificed so much for me,]

34
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:03,160
[and almost died in the hands of Lin Mojiao.]

35
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:07,440
[I didn't contact Lu Xing because I didn't want him to get involved.]

36
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,120
[I didn't expect this to happen.]

37
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,920
I only met Lu Xing once in the Hidden Tower.

38
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,920
If you know

39
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,040
his whereabouts,

40
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,200
please tell me.

41
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:25,400
I'm worried about him.

42
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:27,960
What?

43
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:30,120
You're not satisfied with Lin Moqing,

44
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,760
and you're also interested in Lu Xing?

45
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,920
You're so annoying.

46
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,320
But I tell you,

47
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:39,040
you can't have

48
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,040
either of them.

49
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,720
Maybe you should figure out

50
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,400
who you really care about.

51
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:50,360
Wenjie,

52
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,520
ask your heart.

53
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:58,200
Mind your own business.

54
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:20,440
Look at you, all smiles.

55
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,320
Your brother

56
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,880
must be furious with you.

57
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,520
I'm just

58
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:30,000
fighting fire with fire.

59
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:42,320
What are the conditions?

60
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,320
The other party wants

61
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:48,760
two hundred million.

62
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:51,240
Two hundred million?

63
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:55,640
What a coincidence.

64
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,280
Give him.

65
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,880
Besides these two hundred million,

66
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:08,840
I'll give you another big gift.

67
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:22,040
Do you want to have dinner together tonight?

68
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,120
I have a big gift for you.

69
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:26,840
No.
I'm on a diet.

70
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:32,000
You're not fat.

71
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:33,600
You should eat more.

72
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:35,080
Get fat and go back...

73
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:39,320
I think

74
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,520
you and Miss Blue

75
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,760
must have something going on.

76
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:43,360
What does it have to do with you?

77
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,320
Don't blame me for not warning you.

78
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:47,520
With the way you are now,

79
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,880
what will happen to your plan later?

80
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,880
If she finds out about what you've done...

81
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,200
We'll talk about it later.

82
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:56,840
Talk about it later?

83
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,200
Let's see how you'll explain it.

84
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:08,760
Don't blame me for not reminding you.

85
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:09,920
With the way you are now,

86
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,160
what will happen to the plan later?

87
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:13,240
If she finds out what you've done...

88
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:32,680
This is for you.

89
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:40,480
What is this?

90
00:09:41,680 --> 00:09:42,720
It's not me again, is it?

91
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:45,680
You thought the last doll was ugly, right?

92
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,160
I made a pretty one for you.

93
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,880
Is this pretty?

94
00:09:53,920 --> 00:09:54,400
Of course.

95
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,720
As pretty as you.

96
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:02,480
Stop it.

97
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:04,720
What's the big gift

98
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:06,160
you mentioned last time?

99
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:16,600
Are you

100
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:18,920
willing to...

101
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,840
Is this the big gift?

102
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,120
Xing.

103
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:33,960
I'll take you away.

104
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:49,840
Water.

105
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:55,040
I want water.

106
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:00,120
Give me water.

107
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:22,680
It's all my fault.

108
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:26,280
I shouldn't have trusted Lin Moqing

109
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,200
and lost you.

110
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:34,520
Vivi,
don't worry.

111
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:36,640
I'll find Xu Meng.

112
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:38,880
If you hadn't taken her away,

113
00:13:39,680 --> 00:13:40,960
she wouldn't have disappeared.

114
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:43,560
Trust me,

115
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:44,640
I'll find her.

116
00:13:44,640 --> 00:13:46,400
I trusted you last time

117
00:13:46,560 --> 00:13:47,520
and agreed to work with you.

118
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,040
What about now?

119
00:13:49,280 --> 00:13:50,480
You want me to believe you again?

120
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:52,640
Vivi.

121
00:13:55,760 --> 00:13:56,480
I'm warning you.

122
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:58,440
If anything happens to her,

123
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:00,960
our cooperation will end here.

124
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:03,400
I will also take back the authorization

125
00:14:03,560 --> 00:14:04,800
of the resort.

126
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:35,880
Find Xu Meng

127
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:36,720
at all costs.

128
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:46,200
Xing.

129
00:14:47,040 --> 00:14:47,600
Don't worry.

130
00:14:47,640 --> 00:14:48,640
I know where she is.

131
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:56,000
She must have been here.

132
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:57,480
She must have been moved by Lin Mojiao.
